Reflection(A tiny observation of FOE)
==========================================
Every object in this universe have their own power of reflection.
When a wave collide to some object(the angle of collision and the density of wave always matter) it activate the molecules of object and after reaction the some different wave transmit back is known as reflection.

Our eye look anything because of reflection only.
If the power of reflection is very high one get the almost same image which is transmitted.
Ex- Mirror
If  power of reflection  is very poor ie it absorb the wave almost.
Ex-Black hole, complete dark night.

Reflection can be within and beyond the life.

Beyond the life(Natural/obvious/force less)
--------------------------------------------------------
It is the natural process during transmission of waves in nature.
Ex- 
-Sunlight collide to our body some waves use to produce the vitamin-D in our body and some reflect back.
-The leaf of tree use some part of sunlight to make their food and some part it reflect back.
-Black hole in universe completely absorb  the waves collide with it.
-X-ray machine use the reflection only for image processing.
..so.on..

