ie what happen, which type of waves one receive before and after these reflection.
Here the one receive the waves are almost acceptable by them, it almost match one's thought and emotion/behavior/capability.
Due to matching of frequency of waves it enhance the amplitude frequency of out thought and emotion, ie it make energetic. Due to feeling good once reflection back look like very polite/smooth/light/healthy..so on..

